Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:07.88,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Like a cruel angel{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:14.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become a legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:30.57,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When a blue wind{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Knocks on the door to your heart{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:37.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You just gaze back at me{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And smile oh so gently{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:45.42,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}So eager for something{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You touch so softly{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:52.76,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Those innocent eyes{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:59.48,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But one day, you will realize{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That upon your back{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:07.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You have wings{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You can fly to the faraway future{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.74,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The cruel angel's thesis{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:15.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}One day, you'll take off through a window{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:19.37,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}If your overflowing pathos{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Leads you to betray your memories{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:26.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:30.76,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:56.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I wonder if he's going to{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}skip school again today.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.08,style.default,,0,0,0,,SHINJI'S ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, get up. How long are you\Ngonna stay home from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's been five days already.\NUnit 01 is as good as new.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,Its pilot shouldn't be\Nsitting around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.55,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,TO MS. MISATO KATSURAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.78,style.default,,0,0,0,,He ran away. I guess I can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.13,style.default,,0,0,0,,Er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class as Mr. Ikari.\NOur names are Aida and Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.93,style.default,,0,0,0,,Aida and Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Yes, ma'am! I'm Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.39,style.default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, aren't you the two\Nwho got into Unit 01's entry plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.89,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am! We're really sorry\Nfor any trouble we caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.31,style.default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, we were worried because\NShinji hasn't been to school since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.32,style.default,,0,0,0,,so we thought we'd check in on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:15.65,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Shinji's at Nerv's\Ntraining facility right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:20.78,style.default,,0,0,0,,Um, these study guides\Nhave been piling up on his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.33,style.default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to\Ncome all this way. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,Well, we should be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,Say hi to Mr. Ikari for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll do that. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.09,style.default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,What a babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you little idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.86,style.default,,0,0,0,,TOKYO-3 LOOP LINE NO. 7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.28,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Next stop is Nagao-touge, Nagao-touge.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.04,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Please exit on the right side{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}of the train.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:08.56,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Thank you for using{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Tokyo-3 Loop Line No. 7.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}This train is no longer in service{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}after this stop.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:17.19,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Please remember to collect{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}your belongings before exiting.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,I got to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:31.08,style.default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy! Step right in!\NIt's a real bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.01,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-You really couldn't detect it?!{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-No!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:42.18,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}An object tens of millimeters across{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}struck the South Pole at speeds{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.30,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}in excess of 10% of the speed of light!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.35,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}It was beyond modern science's ability{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to predict, much less prevent!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.93,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But look at what's happening outside!{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}What good is science?!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:56.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Atmospheric flux caused by axial shift{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}has decreased to 3%.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.32,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Has it gotten better outside, then?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:02.15,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No! There's a tsunami on the way!{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Incoming at 230 meters per second!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.57,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Doctor! We must escape!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.99,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No, my duty is to stay here!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.91,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Doctor, dying is easy!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.16,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But you also have a duty{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to bear witness to...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:24.86,style.default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.96,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}He {\c}{\i0}is{\i1\c&Hffffff&} only 14 years old.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.59,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Placing the fate of the human race\Non his shoulders is a lot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,But we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but to have 14-year-olds pilot the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.51,style.default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.89,style.default,,0,0,0,,So, any word from Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:37.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:44.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,None. Maybe he's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.65,style.default,,0,0,0,,-What do you intend to do about it?\N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,He might be better off\Nif he didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.49,style.default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,Well, after the last battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ignore my order?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.83,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Aren't I your operations director?\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:10.05,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's your duty to obey my orders.\NDo you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.13,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Don't let this happen again.\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.72,style.default,,0,0,0,,Is this really getting through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.31,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:21.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,Listen, just repeating\N"Yes, ma'am" isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,I understand just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,But why does it matter? We won.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,It might feel easier to just superficially\Nplay along with what others say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.28,style.default,,0,0,0,,but piloting an Eva with that attitude\Nwill get you killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.58,style.default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:40.08,style.default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say that I'm glad\Nto hear you've got guts,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:43.33,style.default,,0,0,0,,but you're way off base if you think\Nthat will score you points, Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm not fishing for compliments.\NI'm just the only one who can pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.55,style.default,,0,0,0,,So I'll pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.59,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:10:01.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,If piloting the Eva only brings him pain,\Nhe's better off not piloting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,But we need a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.28,style.default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.83,style.default,,0,0,0,,Aida, go on without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:22.79,style.default,,0,0,0,,But I can't leave you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.17,style.default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.56,style.default,,0,0,0,,The new kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,SUMMER TRAINING OVERVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.79,style.default,,0,0,0,,Tohji was sorry he hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.00,style.default,,0,0,0,,I hear his little sister chewed him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,She said it was your robot\Nthat saved us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:17.01,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's hilarious that he got taken\Ndown a peg by a grade-schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.14,style.default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,I like it at night.\NThose cicadas aren't buzzing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.82,style.default,,0,0,0,,It was nice and quiet when I was little,\Nbut there's more every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:35.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato said something about\Nthe ecosystem rebuilding itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,"Ms. Misato," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.33,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.79,style.default,,0,0,0,,You live with a total babe\Nand you get to pilot that Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:49.96,style.default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could pilot the Evangelion\Nall by myself just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:53.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't if I were you.\NYour mother would be worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:59.09,style.default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not a problem.\NI don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,Same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:08.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,-You're hungry, right?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.69,style.default,,0,0,0,,Do you do this a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.69,style.default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.95,style.default,,0,0,0,,Is it training for guerrilla warfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:22.28,style.default,,0,0,0,,What good would toys like this do?\NI'm just having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.39,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.90,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,We're with Nerv Security & Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,We're taking you to HQ under section eight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.49,style.default,,0,0,0,,of the Safety Preservation Ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Will you comply?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.79,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}So you just stood there{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}and let them grab him?!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. Those guys were\NNerv Security & Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:12.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,Pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.96,style.default,,0,0,0,,What's that got to do with it?!\NDon't you have any balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Gross!\N-Weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.38,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:24.01,style.default,,0,0,0,,Only an idiot picks a fight he can't win.\NBalls don't enter into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,-It's been a while.\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,Has wandering around for the last two days\Nmade you feel any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.70,style.default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:47.20,style.default,,0,0,0,,Your Eva is ready and waiting.\NWill you pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:53.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to scold me\Nfor running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,I guess you wouldn't. You're not family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:05.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,What would happen with Unit 01\Nif I didn't pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.31,style.default,,0,0,0,,I suppose Rei would pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.56,style.default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:16.06,style.default,,0,0,0,,How could I do something like that?\NI couldn't force it all on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.90,style.default,,0,0,0,,But you don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:25.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NI'm not cut out for this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.49,style.default,,0,0,0,,But you and Ayanami and Ms. Ritsuko--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:32.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!\NWhat others think doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.42,style.default,,0,0,0,,If you don't really want to, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:38.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the Evas and everything else!\NGo back to your old life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.34,style.default,,0,0,0,,If you keep acting like this,\Nyou're more trouble than you're worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:58.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,The Third Children\Nwill leave Tokyo-3 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,Then rewrite Unit 01's data to match Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.49,style.default,,0,0,0,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.82,style.default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of Unit 00's\Nreactivation trial results,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,we will press on with trials with Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,Reports from the Marduk Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.25,style.default,,0,0,0,,indicate the Fourth Children\Nhas not been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,Meaning that we have\Nno replacement pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.72,style.default,,0,0,0,,Um, where is Ms. Misato?\NI'd like to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:34.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer with Nerv.\NYou're not cleared for that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.95,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Ikari!\N-You forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.50,style.default,,0,0,0,,Um... Can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.22,style.default,,0,0,0,,Um... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.06,style.default,,0,0,0,,Tohji, out with it! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.69,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, I shouldn't have hit you twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,Hit me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.32,style.default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,Please. I wouldn't be able\Nto live with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.99,style.default,,0,0,0,,You know how melodramatic he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.57,style.default,,0,0,0,,Look, if it helps bury the hatchet,\Njust hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.20,style.default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.58,style.default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You don't have much time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.37,style.default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.25,style.default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let me have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,No holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.55,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:07.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,-How did you know I'd be here?\N-Call it a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:11.32,style.default,,0,0,0,,We've said goodbye to dozens\Nof classmates here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:19.29,style.default,,0,0,0,,If you don't stick around, we'll all\Nprobably have to leave town eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,But we can't force you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:26.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,We saw what it's like for you in that Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,I dare anybody to bad-mouth you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.43,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat the crap out of the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.89,style.default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that hangdog look, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Take care.\N-Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:42.73,style.default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.27,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.47,style.default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.51,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be clobbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:19.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm dishonest! And a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:23.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sneak... and a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,Don't give us any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.25,style.default,,0,0,0,,He's gone, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.50,style.default,,0,0,0,,Is this for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.25,style.default,,0,0,0,,The Hedgehog's Dilemma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:53.05,style.default,,0,0,0,,The closer they get,\Nthe more they hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:04.94,style.default,,0,0,0,,He talks like that because he doesn't\Nknow how else to express his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:10.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Limited express maglev bound for Atsugi{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}now arriving on track two.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:15.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}For your safety,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}please stand behind the yellow line.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.28,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The train on track two{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}is an official-use train{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.08,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}departing for Atsugi at 4:20.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The public must remain behind the fence.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:29.09,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Also, the boarding of unauthorized{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}personnel is strictly forbidden.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.17,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Take extra care to obey these rules.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.93,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Keep it up.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.43,style.default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's the babe from Ikari's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:20.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Local train bound for Goura{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}now arriving on track four.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:24.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}For your safety,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}please stand behind the yellow line.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.100,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Passengers with small children,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}please keep a close eye on them.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:36.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The train arriving on track four{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}is the 4:32 local train for Goura.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:40.05,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}All passengers using this train{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}should board and wait.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:46.56,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Train now arriving.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Please step behind the yellow line.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.69,style.default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.48,style.default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.74,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:08.14,style.default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:11.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Rei Ayanami leads a life where her{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}interactions with others are minimal.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:14.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Commander Ikari is the only one{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}she opens up to.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:18.61,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji is perplexed by this girl who{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}is closer to his own father than he is.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:21.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Next episode! "Rei, Beyond the Heart".{\c}{\i0}
